        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2769264340" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8087794386616286098">Loved this book as it was a proper turn pager, and one I did not want to put down! Depicting the saddening tale of two sisters, abused at the hands of their parents, and their escape. I loved how the chapters alternated from the sisters perspectives, showing personal thoughts and feelings as well as events from both of their perspectives and their journeys. Great read, definitely recommend! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

