        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer283803632" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16506446950244280625">This book is one that stays with you for days and days. Like other reviewers I devoured it in less than a day. It is fabulous - the voices of the girls are so real you can hear them speaking as you read. The power of the relationship of the girls extending out beyond the grave is so terribly sad but also comforting for the twin left behind. It made me cry, it made me laugh. Just stunning.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


