  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2440769121?book_show_action=true">Jul 05, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bex Masters" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bex Masters" href="/user/show/16937926-bex-masters">Bex Masters</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title=" 9780141342702" href="/book/show/13005827-black-heart-blue">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2440769121" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16638605447797007208">So I came across this book on eBay held it in my watch list for a good few weeks the cover attracted my attention straight away but had too many books on my list before this but I gave in and ordered it...😀<br/><br/>I absolutely loved this book !! Black heart blue is perfect it touched my heart, I felt so sorry for those poor girls :( this book will definitely stay with me and I will highly recommend it to people. <br/>And happy to say lies like love just arrived in the post :)</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

